low shows historical monthly averages for climate variables in Kutri.\n{{Clear}}\n{{Weather box|collapsed =\n|location = [[Patna Airport]] (1981\u20132010, extremes 1951\u20132012)\n| metric first = Yes\n| single line = Yes\n| Jan record high C = 30.0\n| Feb record high C = 35.1\n| Mar record high C = 41.4\n| Apr record high C = 44.6\n| May record high C = 45.6\n| Jun record high C = 46.6\n| Jul record high C = 41.2\n| Aug record high C = 39.7\n| Sep record high C = 37.5\n| Oct record high C = 37.2\n| Nov record high C = 34.1\n| Dec record high C = 30.5\n| year record high C = 46.6\n| Jan high C = 22.4\n| Feb high C = 26.0\n| Mar high C = 32.2\n| Apr high C = 37.0\n| May high C = 37.4\n| Jun high C = 36.4\n| Jul high C = 33.0\n| Aug high C = 32.9\n| Sep high C = 32.5\n| Oct high C = 31.9\n| Nov high C = 29.0\n| Dec high C = 24.5\n| year high C = 31.3\n| Jan low C = 9.3\n| Feb low C = 12.1\n| Mar low C = 16.7\n| Apr low C = 22.1\n| May low C = 25.1\n| Jun low C = 26.7\n| Jul low C = 26.3\n| Aug low C = 26.3\n| Sep low C = 25.5\n| Oct low C = 21.5\n| Nov low C = 15.1\n| Dec low C = 10.5\n| year low C = 19.8\n| Jan record low C = 1.4\n| Feb record low C = 3.4\n| Mar record low C = 8.2\n| Apr record low C = 13.3\n| May record low C = 17.7\n| Jun record low C = 19.3\n| Jul record low C = 21.1\n| Aug record low C = 20.5\n| Sep record low C = 19.0\n| Oct record low C = 12.0\n| Nov record low C = 7.7\n| Dec record low C = 2.2\n| year record low C = 1.4\n| rain colour = green\n| Jan rain mm = 11.1\n| Feb rain mm = 14.0\n| Mar rain mm = 9.5\n| Apr rain mm = 12.7\n| May rain mm = 43.7\n| Jun rain mm = 162.5\n| Jul rain mm = 354.4\n| Aug rain mm = 277.8\n| Sep rain mm = 197.7\n| Oct rain mm = 49.1\n| Nov rain mm = 7.2\n| Dec rain mm = 6.1\n| year rain mm = 1145.8\n| Jan rain days = 1.2\n| Feb rain days = 1.3\n| Mar rain days = 0.7\n| Apr rain days = 1.0\n| May rain days = 2.9\n| Jun rain days = 6.9\n| Jul rain days = 14.3\n| Aug rain days = 12.5\n| Sep rain days = 9.5\n| Oct ra